results.abstract: conf of young writers, Moscow; Lt Col Gagarin scores nonconformists Yevtushenko, V Aksyonov and A Voznesensky
results.snippet: MOSCOW, May 8 Lieut. Col. Yuri A. Gagarin, the Soviet cosmonaut, has joined the chorus of critics denouncing the popular nonconformist writers Yevgeny Yevtushenko, Vasily Aksyonov and Andrei Voznesensky.

results.abstract: 759 exiles arrive in Fla on ransom ship

headline.main: RANSOM SHIP BRINGS 759 CUBANS TO U.S.

results.snippet: MIAMI, May 18--The United States freighter American Surveyor arrived this morning at Fort Everglades, about 20 miles from Miami, with 759 Cuban refugees aboard.
